title: The Cellar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, International, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A tapas and wine bar with a menu that includes vegetarian items. Tempeh can be substituted for a number of the regular menu items that are not vegetarian. Try the teriyaki tempeh skewers. Worth stopping in when in area or traveling Rt. 17 across the Southern tier of NY state (also visit the Corning Glass Museum and the main shopping area on Market Street).
